    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Training (Taijutsu)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> </p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 20 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b>  | <b>Perform DC:</b> </p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> F</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You must be wearing the cloak at all times while performing this training, and must be suffering from heavy encumbrance due to its weight. The weight, combined with many simple exercises, grants a +4 increase to your maximum Chakra Pool, a +1 inherent bonus to your Strength score, and increases your maximum carrying capacity by 50 lbs, also increasing your light, medium and heavy load capacity by the same amount.<br><br>In addition, you gain a +1 bonus to Strength and Constitution checks, and the penalty to attack rolls induced by encumbrance is reduced by 1, or 2 for heavy encumbrance.</p>\n\n\n\n",
